TypeError: Can't differentiate wrt numpy arrays of dtype object
```

I thought the problem might have to do with the assignment in the the `sgd` function, as I know that assignments to arrays are not supported. But this is an assignment to a list, rather than array, something that seems to work in general.

Any advice? Thanks!

